 target="_blank" data_ue_src="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODg3MzcyMg==&amp;mid=401625960&amp;idx=4&amp;sn=39d890e018413d2145844f4846d7b12d&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect">一只盆的变化......</a></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">❀<a href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODg3MzcyMg==&amp;mid=401625960&amp;idx=5&amp;sn=052d25bce569cd4ede7be60f75e34143&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" target="_blank" data_ue_src="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODg3MzcyMg==&amp;mid=401625960&amp;idx=5&amp;sn=052d25bce569cd4ede7be60f75e34143&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect">【冬季寄养】--12月27日第五次大棚实拍存照反馈</a></p><p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-type="gif" data-ratio="0.04316546762589928" data-w="" width="auto" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/78/85/CgpQU1eQZruAbbagAAAYix-JgN00905414" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/L6HicJ33JTbTcqicWylyknuUXc43Zg5O4CLS984nmOYVZjribEsv9fhakoNGVdlEpnfoGXrfia4ia2VXwyW8nrW9NNA/0?wx_fmt=gif" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p><p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">----呜莎花园</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">接下来正文开启：</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-type="gif" data-ratio="0.11330935251798561" data-w="" width="auto" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/85/CgpQU1eQZryAAvYVAAAkjMO9eds5615257" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/L6HicJ33JTbTcqicWylyknuUXc43Zg5O4CENicXAdicTFSCguic6NuaZlk268DSibOxzkH3WCSicPeyvwPKL3uicQoiaauA/0?wx_fmt=gif" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">为了避免旅途中发生腐烂，网购的肉肉往往都会经历一次非常彻底的脱土、修根、晾根的过程。收到后肉肉势必会经历一个服盆过程，等到新的根系长出来，才能彻底恢复状态。<br></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">所以，网购肉肉的上盆是十分重要的事情，服盆期的养护过程也十分重要。如果处理得当，肉肉可以在几乎不改变状态的情况下完成服盆。如果处理不得当，则有可能状态下滑，很长时间都缓不过来。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">今天我们用示意图来画出不同根系肉肉的上盆方式，希望能帮助花友用最短的时间让肉肉服盆。</p><p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);">一、普通的须根系肉肉</span></strong></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong><strong style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;"><img data-type="gif" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/78/A2/wKjmqVeQZryAbPdQAAATUJm_loQ1752872" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/L6HicJ33JTbQtjZbsO2ib3q2aEaDWowrozEPWNaEIFAryFX5JlPwbP2mr2w1qsQM7ticsFvJUn9KbjHyia1KJHbCsw/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.03597122302158273" data-w=""></strong></strong></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.814748201438849" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/78/85/CgpQU1eQZryAfBhxAAAvU-tSkVM5091763" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aoVXPDyHg1O6ofwJWUWKodzVxq9VECbGRYNy79qTSmEOYkaUhr3ky3icQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">上图是我们常见的景天科肉肉的根系状态，也就是很多须根程伞状分布。但是种植的过程中，有些花友为了让根系能够深入土壤，就把肉肉种植成下图的样子了。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.8794964028776978" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/85/CgpQU1eQZryAGBH0AACJvZkDaoA4033200" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aoCdXHnBrAA3gUV66D05MCH7tCGgJGfUkG59hNHwrmqtTMbOzEIwib3WA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这样的种植方式，会导致根系呼吸产生的废气无法排出来，积累在土壤里就会导致烂根，容易引发黑腐，所以这是一种相当不健康的种植方式。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.9622302158273381" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/78/85/CgpQU1eQZryAe4F1AACKL2edXEI8581812" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aoP8zxMTs0yKHcT5Tu3slWFjGNM8znWKgnvT6TpscXQiaia3gadxtRQHBg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">这是须根系肉肉的正确种植方式。先在花盆里加入一些土壤，让土壤堆积成圆锥形，然后将肉肉的根系散开，再填入土壤固定住根系。这种种植方式最大限度的发挥出根系的效率，能让根系保持透气，利于萌发新根。</p><p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong>二、根系很少的莲座形肉肉</strong></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong><img data-type="gif" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/85/CgpQU1eQZryAY4nOAAATUJm_loQ2467524" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/L6HicJ33JTbQtjZbsO2ib3q2aEaDWowrozEPWNaEIFAryFX5JlPwbP2mr2w1qsQM7ticsFvJUn9KbjHyia1KJHbCsw/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.03597122302158273" data-w=""><br></strong></span><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.45323741007194246" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/78/A2/wKjmqVeQZryAbNmhAAAfdKS3zBg6527084" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aoZBRknV103JkQmCCc6yfW7ygN1zQq1Bz63YP4RPbR4V5KxU6TrhSTSA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">上图是莲座形的无根或者少根的砍头肉肉，这种肉肉放于土表后常常发生不生根或者表面真菌感染的情况，容易造成生根失败。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.8758992805755396" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/A2/wKjmqVeQZr2ADK4kAACEvYWAHHo0163961" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05ao3YmgCtyGGGclKKcKxbMenfv9IDIff2IsE2STR4NoicCrOKKtnz1u7dw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">正确的种植方式是在土壤的表面挖一个坑，刚好可以让肉肉的<span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong>茎部离土壤很近而又不接触土壤</strong></span>。这样，新根就可以在既潮湿又透气的空间里萌发成长，然后轻松的钻入土壤里。</p><p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong>三、粗而长的营养根肉肉</strong></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong><strong style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;"><img data-type="gif" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/A2/wKjmqVeQZr2AGfVgAAATUJm_loQ6625860" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/L6HicJ33JTbQtjZbsO2ib3q2aEaDWowrozEPWNaEIFAryFX5JlPwbP2mr2w1qsQM7ticsFvJUn9KbjHyia1KJHbCsw/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.03597122302158273" data-w=""></strong></strong></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.9748201438848921" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/86/CgpQU1eQZr2AKdy_AAA6OXdOAC87201701" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aoaicPK3GVdGOFLeH2ILpjF0IIgrxUTTEiadAicQKJ9udkqPsW7xDej1KYw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">上图这类根系叫做营养根。常见的玉露就属于此类根系。营养根的特点是又粗又长，白白净净的，很容易脱土。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">有的花友拿到这类根系，觉得根系太长了，远远超过了花盆的深度，就把根系剪断了，这是很不科学的做法。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">一来营养根里有很多营养物质，是肉肉辛辛苦苦积攒起来的，剪断不利于肉肉后期的生长。二来营养根截面很粗，如果剪断，需要晾根非常长的时间肉肉才能完全修复创面，这时候如果急于上盆种植，就可能导致烂根的发生。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.7805755395683454" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/A2/wKjmqVeQZr2AY_yZAABsxxpjM_o7793947" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aobJpU5FP2TGGBgfsJeGFruTg6BWCsnuKqF0saxXteUwdgWSGN8faO8A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">对于粗而长的营养根，正确的种植方式，是先在花盆里铺少量土壤，然后将营养根盘曲在花盆里，尽量让根系互相分开，然后填上土壤即可。当有更大更合适的盆子就更好了。</p><p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong>四、少根或者无根的老桩肉肉</strong></span></p><p><strong style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;"><img data-type="gif" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/86/CgpQU1eQZr2AGG8fAAATUJm_loQ8850155" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/L6HicJ33JTbQtjZbsO2ib3q2aEaDWowrozEPWNaEIFAryFX5JlPwbP2mr2w1qsQM7ticsFvJUn9KbjHyia1KJHbCsw/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.03597122302158273" data-w=""></strong></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">最后说说那些没根或者少根的老桩肉肉。文章开头被花友剪掉根系的山地玫瑰也属于此类。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.591726618705036" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/78/86/CgpQU1eQZr2ADajmAAAeXIQc2Cs5176256" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aoToKt80yfu1nbo8aKYKz4mhJiczg8Xn0jsPeqIE8DdxAxcybahDPKGVA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">因为没有根系，所以我们会发现这类肉肉怎么种都难以立在花盆里站稳。所以大多数花友都是采用了深埋的方式种植。对于这类肉肉，深埋发根确实是正确的做法，但是，深埋容易造成肉肉茎部不够透气，导致茎部发生黑腐。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.8489208633093526" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M01/78/86/CgpQU1eQZr6AH8q9AAB5AYDrdT49011087" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aovYsNWib3kj2DNo6IkY0bhhSfyaIwSwER7IzgMXQP2Gg2gicWLAmn85OA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以我么需要用下图中的方法来帮助肉肉的茎部透气。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.8776978417266187" data-w="" src="http://pic.kuaizhan.com/g1/M00/78/A2/wKjmqVeQZr6AcGY3AACDVNCnEDM6640019" wx_src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/7AUfBesBibpV8NccgrzKjiaaQPMEwW05aorEnhQEIW9NustFOBGXXVlKtPrCSKxsbyjySpibzv0tttNokvgCPTepQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">这个方法很像是铺一个很厚的面。就是先装半盆土壤，然后将无根的老桩轻轻放在土壤表面，不埋土。然后填入大颗粒赤玉土或者麦饭石之类的清洁透气的植料，填入的深度以能固定住整颗肉肉为准。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">这个方法的好处就是让肉肉的茎部处于潮湿但很透气的环境当中。当新根萌发时，可以顺利的钻入底层的土壤中吸取养分，同时肉肉也能得到很好的固定。</p><p><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">总结一下，不管是哪一种根系，我们的<span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170);"><strong>目标都是不变的：那就是潮湿和透气兼顾</strong></span>。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;">如果上了盆不浇水，那就跟裸根放在那里不种植也没什么区别。任何一种肉肉在上盆前都需要经过充分的晾根。晾根的时间可以简单粗略的套用公式，那就是被剪断的根部截面直径，每毫米晾根1天。这样来说，一棵根部断面5毫米的肉肉，就需要在散光环境下晾根5天才行。上盆的过程中，由于根部与土壤发生摩擦，所以多多少少会产生一些小伤口。上盆以后过24小时再浇水的目的也是为了防止黑腐。</p><p style="line-height: 1.5em;"><br></p><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">欢迎“写留言”和大家一起互动，让世界听到你的声音！<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong></p><hr style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作者</span></strong><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">：</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(15, 36, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">呜莎花园</span></span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-wid